description: Physitrack PLC is a GB-based company operating in  industry. Physitrack PLC, formerly Physitrack Ltd, is a United Kingdom-based is a digital healthcare company. The firm provides solution for patient engagement that includes clinical home exercise and education prescription, outcomes tracking and Telehealth for physical rehabilitation and prevention. Its business lines include software as a service (SaaS) based software platform tailored to the needs of healthcare providers and physiotherapists, enabling the digitalization of the patient journey, from initial contact to patient interactions and outcomes tracking, and a virtual care to offer remote physiotherapy on demand by using the its technology platform. Its SaaS offering has paying healthcare provider users and registered patients. Its software suite also comprises an in-house developed Telehealth solution and a digital exercise library on a technology platform based on Amazon Web Services (AWS) cloud architecture.
